column2: wolNPChla_plot_bachman <- ggplot(data = wol_bachman_NPchla, aes(x=P, y=chla)) + geom_point() + theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, vjust = 0.5, hjust=1)) + ggtitle("P (mg/L) vs Chla (ug/L) in West Okoboji Lake From Bachman") + geom_smooth(method=lm) + xlab("P (mg/L)") + ylab("Chlorophyll a (ug/L)")
